MobileStorm,provides,web,based,marketing,platform,for,businesses,interested,in,reaching,out,to,a,wide,variety,of,audiences,through,multiple,communication,channels,such,as,email,mobile,apps,SMS,and,social,media,Other,services,provided,by,MobileStorm,include,campaign,reporting,and,analysis,database,management,and,reporting,and,on,demand,support,The,MobileStorm,API,is,only,open,to,those,who,have,an,account,with,service,As,such,much,information,about,the,workings,of,the,API,is,hidden,MobileStorm,advertises,many,features,of,their,web,based,marketing,API,including,messaging,reporting,keyword,management,data,validation,push,notification,and,general,data,management